00:39:39.803 --> 00:39:44.360
So the proficiency of the
experts should in no way

00:39:44.360 --> 00:39:49.630
inform the rest of us as
to our ability to do it.

00:39:49.630 --> 00:39:52.180
Moreover, if you're driving
on a Sunday afternoon

00:39:52.180 --> 00:39:55.660
past a high school,
basketball hoops outside,

00:39:55.660 --> 00:39:57.920
