00:40:00.370 --> 00:40:01.745
But you go to the
farmer's market

00:40:01.745 --> 00:40:03.750
and you hear some 35,
40-year-old singing

00:40:03.750 --> 00:40:05.750
and you probably immediately
start judging them.

00:40:05.750 --> 00:40:08.089
